{"tid":1171967,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[真真假假]外媒爆 Marvel 正考慮將死侍引入《蜘蛛俠3》","createTime":"2019-05-26T05:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T05:29:35.000Z","uid":105567,"like":44,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"b1eee321bce3db7257a4071928ffa66fd9d67ff8","tid":1171967,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T05:52:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://gank.fanpiece.com/gamelife/%E5%A4%96%E5%AA%92%E7%88%86-Marvel-%E6%AD%A3%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E5%B0%87%E6%AD%BB%E4%BE%8D%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5-%E8%9C%98%E8%9B%9B%E4%BF%A03-c1349108.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgank.fanpiece.com%2Fgamelife%2F%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%25AA%2592%25E7%2588%2586-Marvel-%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BE%258D%25E5%25BC%2595%25E5%2585%25A5-%25E8%259C%2598%25E8%259B%259B%25E4%25BF%25A03-c1349108.html&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFC8TOYGSXSADKPC8%2B0d5FCk%3D&h=7a75a579\" target=\"_blank\">https://gank.fanpiece.com/gamelife/%E5%A4%96%E5%AA%92%E7%88%86-Marvel-%E6%AD%A3%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E5%B0%87%E6%AD%BB%E4%BE%8D%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5-%E8%9C%98%E8%9B%9B%E4%BF%A03-c1349108.html</a><br />\n<br />\n自迪士尼收購 Fox 後，不少 Marvel 迷都非常期待 X-Men及死侍回MCU，雖然官方稱 X-Men 將重新選角，但死侍卻被留下來，而近日就有外國傳媒爆料 Marvel 正考慮將死侍引入MCU，而目前就主要有三個方案。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1.制作新電影,例如《死侍3》</strong><br />\n《死侍》整體成績都相當不錯，之前死侍(Ryan Reynolds)也說會有《死侍3》，但由於迪士尼的形象，死侍很難能繼續保持以往風格，而且如果不是限制級，電影也肯定大打折扣！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2.Disney+</strong><br />\n即將上線的「Disney+」，即使未能這麼快製作電影，作為 Disney+ 的限定劇集也不錯，網劇的題材也相對寬鬆，也能測試一下觀眾反應。<br />\n<br />\n3.客串演出<br />\n很早以前蜘蛛俠(Tom Holland)曾透露自己跟 Marvel 簽下三部曲電影，而死侍在漫畫中跟蜘蛛俠也有相當多交情，假如能在《蜘蛛俠3》回歸，相信更多粉絲期待！<br />\n<br />\n來源：unilad"},{"pid":"64e93c74c11ca8670a4aa941fea88516b2c5004a","tid":1171967,"uid":6026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T06:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /